<template>
  <v-data-table
    :headers="headers"
    :items="data"
    multi-sort
    item-key="full_name"
    class="table-rounded"
  >
    <!-- status -->
    <template v-slot:item.statusCode="{ item }">
      <v-chip
        small
        :color="statusColor[status[item.statusCode]]"
        class="font-weight-medium"
      >
        {{ status[item.statusCode] }}
      </v-chip>
    </template>

    <!-- status -->
    <template v-slot:item.valid="{ item }">
      <v-chip
        small
        :color="statusColor[status[item.valid]]"
        class="font-weight-medium"
      >
        {{ status[item.valid] }}
      </v-chip>
    </template>
  </v-data-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
    headers: Array,
    data: Array,
    statusColor: Object,
    status: Object,
    statusPropertyName: String,
  },
};
</script>
